briefTitle: A Study to Evaluate the Immunogenicity of Quadrivalent LAIV in Adults 18 to 49 Years of Age
officialTitle: A Randomized, Double-Blind, Active Controlled Study to Evaluate the Immunogenicity of MEDI3250 in Adults 18 to 49 Years of Age
conditions: Healthy or Stable Underlying Chronic Medical Condition
summary: The objective of this study was to show that quadrivalent live attenuated influenza vaccine (Q/LAIV; MEDI3250) produced antibody levels similar to those produced by the commercial vaccine, FluMist.

primaryOutcome.measure: The 4 Post-dose Strain-specific Serum Hemagglutination Inhibition (HAI) Antibody Geometric Mean Titers (GMT) in the Q/LAIV (MEDI3250) Arm Are Noninferior to Those in the Comparator FluMist Group.
